{"tid":1471912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非心聲］其實做香港人好慘","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:52:26.000Z","uid":266777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"715fdfdbec7df29482591efd7a7820ee14e8d6b8","tid":1471912,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:49:28.000Z","msg":"其實香港人永遠都係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">二等人</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論係而家既中國定舊時既英國</span></span></strong><br />\n佢地只係想喺識生金蛋既香港拎著數<br />\n冇一邊真係真心<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重視香港</span><br />\n好開心咁多手足出力出時間出金錢去將成個抗爭推高<br />\n請大家繼續用所有認為可行既方法各自爬山<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堅持到底</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永不割蓆</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港加油</span>"},{"pid":"5ae23c62477eb758b10f555204198de8146e1117","tid":1471912,"uid":266777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}